    <abstract>
      <t>   The existing EVPN multi-homing load-balancing modes do not adequately
   represent ethernet-segments facing access networks with Layer-2
   Gateway protocols such as G.8032, (M)STP, etc.  This document defines
   a new multi-homing mechanism to support these loop-preventing Layer-2
   protocols.

	 </t>
